serving as the lord here. I look forward to

Gilcho told me most of it. About the incident
during the demon attack, where you completely

Truly a savior. Thank you for protecting the town.

I'm not exactly sure why I have that kind of

power came over me...

light and hope for us.

I can only express my gratitude for your
reincarnation.

I believe there must be a reason behind my
reincarnation here. I need to find out what I
should accomplish in this place. If I can become a
source of hope, there's nothing better than that.

I think I mentioned this before, but the power of
you magical girls is the only power that can
oppose the demons. It would be great if we could
fight together somehow.

Of course, I will fight. This power is surely
meant for that. I will find the demon's stronghold
and launch a full-scale attack from here.

...! It's truly reliable... However, they are also
formidable... The battle won't be so easy.

We know that their stronghold is the Astaloth
Labyrinth, located beyond the magical inferno zone
to the northeast. We know that, but we still don't
know how to break through there.

If they are coming from there, there must be some
kind of secret passage. I need to find out...

In this Grimoire Land, there are four Lolimon
leaders who govern different regions. It would be
good to gather information from those leaders.

And I've heard that the leaders are currently
facing various problems. If we can help resolve
them, they might become even more of an asset to
us.

Understood. I will do my best to explore Grimoire
Land and find a way to open the path to the demon
stronghold.

It has been hundreds of years since this state has
continued, but to overturn it... Could it be...
the savior for that?

It is said that long ago, when the first magical
girl was reincarnated in a distant continent from
this Grimoire Land, they greatly changed the
course of the great war against the demons with
their immense power...
Perhaps, you might be the reincarnation of that...

If anything else happens, make sure to come to me
and do your best, Konoha.

And this is a small token of gratitude. Please
accept it and make use of it for your future
activities.

Thank you very much, Lord Candira. I will do my
best!
Have you seen? There aren't many people like that.

Probably... but it would be troublesome to change
the current situation... Hell, don't take your
eyes off her.

In case anything happens, make sure to inform all
the executives about this.

legends.
